## 🧾 Additional Terms and Conditions

This Graylog logging hook is part of the **HydrAIDE SDK**, developed by
**Gebri Péter** and **Trendizz Systems**, and serves as a pluggable log interface
for **HydrAIDE Core** and **HydrAIDE Server** systems.

